N\geq2
\mu=\frac{1}{N}\sum_{i=1}^{N}i = \frac{N+1}{2}
\sigma^2=\frac{1}{N}\sum_{i=1}^{N} (x_i-\mu)^2 = \frac{N^2-1}{12}
E[Y|X]=\frac{N\mu-X}{N-1}
